Package edu.uci.ics.jung.io.graphml.parser

Interface Summary
ElementParser Interface for all element parsers.
 

Class Summary
AbstractElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Base class for element parsers - provides some minimal functionality.
DataElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses the data element.
EdgeElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses an edge element.
ElementParserRegistry<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Registry for all element parsers.
EndpointElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses endpoint elements.
GraphElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses graph elements.
GraphMLEventFilter Filter to ignore unsupported XML events.
HyperEdgeElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses hyper edge elements.
KeyElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses key elements.
NodeElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses node elements.
ParserContext<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Provides resources related to the current parsing context.
PortElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses port elements.
StringElementParser<G extends Hypergraph<V,E>,V,E> Parses an element that just contains text.
UnknownElementParser Skips an entire unknown subtree of the XML
